name: Project Timebreaker
description:
Make a mad dash for the portal at the end of the level!

Find and master the fastest route!

Features:

  • 1 unique level!
  • Jumping!
  • Enemies!
  • Speedrunning!

Can you beat the dev?

Try to beat 22.98!

Music is from Three Red Hearts by Abstraction. You can find their music here:

http://abstractionmusic.com/

Made for One Game a Month #1! Theme: Time is Key
